{
  "text": "To establish the Baxter equation (47) for the operator (50), we will use the Gaudin-Pasquier trick [CITATION_1] . It relies on transformation properties of the elements of the monodromy matrix under a gauge transformation of the Lax operators, It will be convenient to choose M j in the form",
